First Department,

October, 1958

(October 2, 1958) In the Matter of Arthur P. McNulty, Appellant, against Robert C. Weaver, as State Rent Administrator, Respondent, and Kenneth V. Wagenbach et al., Intervenors-Respondents.

Order unanimously affirmed, with $20 costs and disbursements to the respondents. No opinion. Concur — Botein, P. J., Breitel, Rabin, Valente, and McNally, JJ.
